### Suggestion Structure
```python
class Suggestion:
    """A single AI-generated suggestion."""

    suggestion_id: str
    suggestion_type: SuggestionType  # EFFECT, PARAMETER, TRANSITION, TIMELINE
    effect_type: Optional[str]
    parameters: Dict[str, float]
    confidence: float  # 0.0-1.0
